earch investigating experiences of advance decision making (ADM) in people with BP or their attitudes towards it. Therefore an online survey of BPUKâ€™s mailing list was conducted. 932 people with BP completed the survey (response rate 5.61%). Here we present (a) the questionnaire designed specifically for this study and (b) the study's supplementary information (generation of outcomes of interest, missing data analysis and cross-tabulations of outcomes of interest with independent variables)"}}]},{"typeName":"subject","multiple":true,"typeClass":"controlledVocabulary","value":["Medicine, Health and Life Sciences"]},{"typeName":"keyword","multiple":true,"typeClass":"compound","value":[{"keywordValue":{"typeName":"keywordValue","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"Surveys and Questionnaires"},"keywordVocabulary":{"typeName":"keywordVocabulary","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"MeSH"},"keywordVocabularyURI":{"typeName":"keywordVocabularyURI","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"https://www.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/"}},{"keywordValue":{"typeName":"keywordValue","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"Bipolar Disorder"},"keywordVocabulary":{"typeName":"keywordVocabulary","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"MeSH"},"keywordVocabularyURI":{"typeName":"keywordVocabularyURI","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"https://www.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/"}},{"keywordValue":{"typeName":"keywordValue","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"Bipolar and Related Disorder"},"keywordVocabulary":{"typeName":"keywordVocabulary","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"MeSH"},"keywordVocabularyURI":{"typeName":"keywordVocabularyURI","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"https://www.nlm.nih.gov/mesh/"}},{"keywordValue":{"typeName":"keywordValue","multiple":false,"typeClass":"primitive","value":"Advance Care Planning"},"keywordVocabulary":{"typeName":"keywordVocabulary","multiple":false,"typeClass":